        <div class="flex-col items-start gap-5 inline-flex px-2 md:px-6 py-6 md:py-2">
            <div class="w-full text-lg font-normal">For a Local Restaurant, We deployed a chatbot that increased customer engagement, leading to a 30% rise in bookings within three months.</div>
