                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-col items-start gap-5 inline-flex px-2 md:px-6 py-6 md:py-2">
            <div class="w-full text-lg font-normal">For a B2B Software Company, Our automation service streamlined client communications, boosting response rates by 40% and reducing manual workload by 60%..</div>
            <div class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
